ORLY partners with WANNA NAILS and introduces Augmented Reality nail colors!
ORLY’s Fall 2018 collection is the first of a range of new nail colors that will debut on Wanna Nail that will allow the consumer to preview in real-time before purchasing. Wanna Nails users can browse the many nail polish shades using a phone camera aimed at their hand. While in app, the colors can be changed on the fly, Boomerang-style videos can be created, and users can take selfies as if their hands were freshly manicured.
Make sure you'll test out our new update and try real-time video manicure. No more confusion! Also,​ check out new ORLY autumn shades.
